    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Both R1 findings addressed in 3b139bbf7. Poll conditions switched to exclusion pattern (`!= Pending && != Running`), callbacks now name and use the passed context. Three reviewers independently verified both fixes and re-reviewed the full diff. Bisky confirmed no sibling subtests need the same guard. All ran the test under `-race` with clean results.\n\n\"The exclusion pattern is more robust because the set of processing states is smaller and more stable than the set of terminal states.\" (Meruem)\n\n> \ud83e\udd16 This review was automatically generated with Coder Agents.",
